    "summary": "We propose a type of all-optical switch which consists of two periodically\ncurved nonlinear optical waveguides placed in parallel. Compared to the\nall-optical switch based on the traditional nonlinear directional coupler with\nstraight waveguides, this all-optical switch has much lower switching threshold\npower and sharper switching width.", 
